sub_title: Team Lead | API Management at KLM Royal Dutch Airlines
summary:
Passionate software engineer with a diverse international experience, having worked for companies in Azerbaijan, Germany, and the Netherlands. Extensive experience in the banking sector, airlines, and delivery (location) domains. Specializing in backend development, API design, clean code and clan architecture practices. Proficient in backend, mobile and devops technologies. 
Accomplished team manager with a proven track record of leading and inspiring teams ranging from 5 to 31 people.
